    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Older vehicle in poor condition and priced accordingly. It shows heavy cosmetic wear inside and out, with noticeable age-related deterioration, visible imperfections, and signs of deferred maintenance. Buyers should expect that it will likely need repairs and reconditioning before it can be counted on as a dependable daily driver. Best suited for someone looking for a budget vehicle, a project, or something to fix up.",
