    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Clean, well-kept classic in good overall condition with an honest, appealing presentation and the kind of cared-for feel that makes it easy to enjoy right away. It shows nicely throughout, with solid paint, a tidy interior, and good driver-quality character, while still leaving room for the next owner to take it to the next level if desired. A strong, enjoyable vintage car that presents well and should make a rewarding addition to any garage.",
      "price": 32900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable transportation at an affordable price. This vehicle offers a practical opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer seeking a straightforward car with plenty of value left to give. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a solid option for commuting, errands, or as a first car. Priced to move and presented with transparency, this is a smart buy for someone who wants inexpensive, usable transportation without unnecessary frills.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without spending a fortune? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and can still be a great fit for someone who wants basic transportation, a project, or a handy backup vehicle. Priced with its age and condition in mind, it offers a straightforward chance to get on the road for less. If you\u2019re after honest value and don\u2019t mind a car with a few stories to tell, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid, honest driver with great project potential and a surprisingly stout mechanical feel. The engine pulls cleanly, the drivetrain feels robust, and it has the kind of straightforward, usable character that makes it an excellent budget entry or weekend fixer-upper. Cosmetically it shows its age and needs attention, but the core package is there: dependable running gear, usable cabin, and a platform that still has plenty left to give for the next owner willing to put in a little work. Hard to find something this complete with this much upside at this price.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap entry point. Honest poor-condition car priced to move fast. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with honest character and a story in every mile, this ride has the kind of presence that makes it feel like more than simple transportation. It\u2019s an affordable chance to get behind the wheel of something with grit, charm, and plenty of potential\u2014perfect for someone who appreciates a budget-friendly driver, a weekend tinkering project, or a practical set of wheels with personality. If you like vehicles that have lived a little and still have more road ahead, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
